      "markdown": "\u003cdiv class=\"api-reference-page\">\n  \u003cdiv class=\"api-reference-main\">\n    \u003cp class=\"eyebrow\">threads\u003c/p>\n    \u003ch1>Delete thread\u003c/h1>\n    \n\u003cp class=\"api-description\">Delete a thread and all its messages.\u003c/p>\n    \u003cdiv class=\"api-route-row\">\n      \u003cspan class=\"api-method api-method-delete\">DELETE\u003c/span>\n      \u003ccode>/api/v1/threads/{id}/\u003c/code>\n      \u003cbutton class=\"copy-button\" type=\"button\" data-copy-value=\"/api/v1/threads/{id}/\" aria-label=\"Copy API path\">Copy\u003c/button>\n    \u003c/div>\n    \u003csection class=\"api-section\">\u003ch2>Headers\u003c/h2>\n\u003cdiv class=\"api-param\">\n    \u003cdiv>\u003ccode>Authorization\u003c/code>\u003cspan class=\"api-required\">required\u003c/span>\u003c/div>\n    \u003cp>any - API key authentication using Bearer scheme\u003c/p>\n  \u003c/div>\u003ch2>Path Parameters\u003c/h2>\n\u003cdiv class=\"api-param\">\n    \u003cdiv>\u003ccode>id\u003c/code>\u003cspan class=\"api-required\">required\u003c/span>\u003c/div>\n    \u003cp>string\u003c/p>\n  \u003c/div>\u003c/section>\n    \n    \u003csection class=\"api-section\">\n    \u003ch2>Response\u003c/h2>\n    \u003cp>No response body\u003c/p>\n    \u003cdiv class=\"api-param\">\u003cdiv>\u003ccode>any\u003c/code>\u003c/div>\u003c/div>\n  \u003c/section>\n  \u003c/div>\n  \u003caside class=\"api-example-panel\">\n    \u003cdiv class=\"api-example-block\">\n      \u003cdiv class=\"api-example-heading\">\u003cspan>cURL\u003c/span>\u003cbutton class=\"copy-button copy-button-dark\" type=\"button\" data-copy-code aria-label=\"Copy cURL example\">Copy\u003c/button>\u003c/div>\n      \u003cpre>\u003ccode data-api-curl-code data-api-curl-method=\"DELETE\" data-api-curl-path=\"/api/v1/threads/{id}/\">curl --request DELETE \\\n  --url https://api.camelai.com/api/v1/threads/{id}/ \\\n  --header &#039;Authorization: Bearer &lt;token&gt;&#039;\u003c/code>\u003c/pre>\n    \u003c/div>\n    \u003cdiv class=\"api-example-block\">\n      \u003cdiv class=\"api-example-heading\">\u003cspan>200\u003c/span>\u003cbutton class=\"copy-button copy-button-dark\" type=\"button\" data-copy-code aria-label=\"Copy response example\">Copy\u003c/button>\u003c/div>\n      \u003cpre>\u003ccode>&quot;&lt;unknown&gt;&quot;\u003c/code>\u003c/pre>\n    \u003c/div>\n  \u003c/aside>\n\u003c/div>"
